  "texts": [
    "These principles are based on a deep understanding of both the technical capabilities of generative AI and the nuances of human language and cognition.",
    "In this regard, this paper introduces 10 principles and 15 strategies that refer to 'Prompt Engineering for Gen [i] erative AI Framework' to unleash your prompts and, metaphorically, make your wishes true.",
    "Accordingly:",
    "Explore and Comprehend the Model's Capabilities: Familiarize yourself with the strengths and limitations of the generative AI model to create prompts that leverage its areas of expertise.",
    "Avoid queries that are too complex or specialized, which may fall outside the model's training."
  ]
}